room_title: Escape room "Once Upon A Time" by Red Door Escape Room in Sacramento
room_description: Step into the fairy tale world of heroes and kings as you travel in time and space to a magical kingdom! You've been called upon because your help is desperately needed here. The treasury was broken into by Rumpelstiltskin. Not only are the most valuable artifacts missing, they can be used for enacting a curse on the kingdom. Stop him before the deadly ritual is complete!
